# ── Whitelist policy ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This working directory also holds GBs of openEMS/FDTD run output and a
# copyrighted reference paper PDF. Rather than enumerate every generated
# artifact, ignore EVERYTHING at the top level and re-include only source/design
# files. New simulation output directories are therefore excluded automatically.
# (Note: git .gitignore has NO trailing/inline comments — keep comments on their
#  own lines, or the pattern silently includes the comment text.)

# ignore all top-level entries by default
/*

# ...but keep source, docs, and the KiCad project:
# .py  openEMS/Python builders, characterizers, DE optimizers
# .m   MATLAB antenna scripts
# .md  design notes / run guides
# .ps1 watchdog
# .png small top-level geometry visualizations
!.gitignore
!README.md
!*.py
!*.m
!*.md
!*.ps1
!*.png
!*.kicad_pcb
!*.kicad_pro
!*.kicad_prl
!*.kicad_sch
!fp-lib-table
!Parts.pretty/

# Never publish, regardless of the rules above:
#   *.pdf  -> the copyrighted reference paper (Ding et al.) stays local
#   sim run data, checkpoints, logs, caches all live in ignored output dirs
*.pdf
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pkl
*.h5
*.vtk
*.npz
